{"title":"今天发下土地证","authors":["彭斐"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":2,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天发下土地证"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彭斐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天发下了土地证。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺老汉全家真高兴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红腾腾“官印”盖在当中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政府保障咱财产所有权，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣布从今后地权已确定。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“千年文约会说话！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺分亩实报，四至填清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给俺翻了身的人留下凭证。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×　　　×　　　×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全家大小每人都有份，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把俺老婆子的名字也填上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那工作同志问她“唤啥？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还羞的她老脸通红！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——现在世道真“兴”的好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活了多半辈，妇女才真正成了“人”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×　　　×　　　×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想从前，卖地给老财："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划十字、捺指印，实在心痛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到现在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党领导咱分下土地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政府又给咱发下土地证。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往后，咱就能在自己的土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好好耕种。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺赶快把它用布包好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交给老婆子牢牢的藏在柜中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺全家人更加要勤劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心发财致富闹好光景！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}